@startuml
title Where casp sits: sale system, POI, and acquirer
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FCEBE3
  BorderColor #C85C3C
}
skinparam ArrowColor #C85C3C
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FCEBE3
skinparam noteBorderColor #C85C3C

actor Cardholder as CH
[Sale system\n(cash register)] as SALE
[POI\n(payment terminal)] as POI
[Acquirer host] as ACQ

CH --> POI : presents card
SALE --> POI : casp service / device requests
POI --> SALE : casp responses and events
POI --> ACQ : cain / canm to the acquirer
note bottom of POI : casp is the sale-to-POI leg only;\nthe POI talks to the acquirer separately
@enduml
